<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>تَفْسِيرُ سُورَةِ الْقَمَر<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٤٢:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {اقْتَرَبَتِ السَّاعَةُ وَانْشَقَّ الْقَمَرُ <span class="c2">(١)</span> وَإِنْ يَرَوْا آيَةً يُعْرِضُوا وَيَقُولُوا سِحْرٌ مُسْتَمِرٌّ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> وَكَذَّبُوا وَاتَّبَعُوا أَهْوَاءَهُمْ وَكُلُّ أَمْرٍ مُسْتَقِرٌّ <span class="c2">(٣)</span> وَلَقَدْ جَاءَهُمْ مِنَ الْأَنْبَاءِ مَا فِيهِ مُزْدَجَرٌ <span class="c2">(٤)</span>} <span class="c4">[القمر: ١ - ٤]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ:</span> <span class="c3">{مُسْتَمِرٌّ}</span>: <span class="c2">«ذَاهِبٌ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ:</span> <span class="c3">{مُزْدَجَرٌ}</span>: <span class="c2">«مُتَنَاهٍ»</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>